  "description": "Introducing the Ubiquiti UniFi Express, a revolutionary device that combines the power of a cloud gateway and a Wi-Fi 6 access point, all packed into a compact and sleek form factor. Whether you're setting up a new network or expanding your existing one, the UX is the ideal solution for seamless connectivity and powerful performance. With UniFi Express, you can effortlessly power your entire network or simply mesh as an access point, delivering exceptional performance and stability wherever you need it.",
  "detailed_description": [
    {
      "heading": "Seamless Network Experience",
      "text": "Introducing the Ubiquiti UniFi Express, a revolutionary device that combines the power of a cloud gateway and a Wi-Fi 6 access point, all packed into a compact and sleek form factor. Whether you're setting up a new network or expanding your existing one, the UX is the ideal solution for seamless connectivity and powerful performance. With UniFi Express, you can effortlessly power your entire network or simply mesh as an access point, delivering exceptional performance and stability wherever you need it."
    },
    {
      "heading": "Key Features",
      "text": "UniFi Express features 140 m² single-unit coverage, ensuring that your devices stay connected even in larger spaces. Experience the next generation of Wi-Fi with built-in WiFi6 (2x2 MIMO) technology, capable of supporting up to 60+ connected Wi-Fi devices simultaneously. Seamlessly manage up to four additional UniFi Network devices when operated as a gateway, centralizing control over the entire network. The UX is equipped with a Gigabit Ethernet WAN port for connecting to your internet provider and a Gigabit Ethernet LAN port for expanding your network."
    },
    {
      "heading": "Manage Your Network with Ease",
      "text": "Leverage the UniFi Network 8.0.7 and later management software to easily configure, monitor, and optimize your network performance. A 0.96\" LCD status display provides real-time information about the device's status and settings. UniFi Express features the enhanced security, providing your network with WPA3 security protocols and safeguarding your connected devices."
    }
  ],
